                    srcset="https://img.assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/20210114-trump-deficit-1x1.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=105&amp;q=75&amp;w=105&amp;s=0e60d90543df8b4989af5ec5cc733ca4 105w, https://img.assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/20210114-trump-deficit-1x1.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=210&amp;q=75&amp;w=210&amp;s=e4aa97b6956735686d5f910733a916cb 210w"
                    width="105"
                    height="105"
                    loading="lazy"
                    js-autosizes
                />
            </a>
        </div>
    
    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/a-closer-look">A Closer Look</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/national-debt-trump">
                                    Trump Built a National Debt So Big That It’ll Weigh Down the Economy for Years
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            The “King of Debt” promised to reduce the national debt — then his tax cuts made it surge. Add in the pandemic, and he oversaw the third-biggest deficit increase of any president.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/allan-sloan">Allan Sloan</a>, ProPublica, and <span class="name">Cezary Podkul</span> for <a href="https://www.propublica.org">ProPublica</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2021-01-14EST05:00">Jan. 14, 2021, 5 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                            </div>
                    <div class="most-read-story">
                                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    

                    
                    
    
        <div class="lead-art thumbnail">
            <a class="aspect-1-1" href="https://www.propublica.org/article/flint-michigan-water-crisis-ten-years-after">
                <img
                    alt=""
                    src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271%27%20height%3D%271%27%20style%3D%27background%3Atransparent%27%2F%3E"
                    srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20240208-Maney-Flint-029_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.4423&amp;fp-y=0.4976&amp;h=105&amp;q=75&amp;w=105&amp;s=ab7c96855142a666721b9d123753b298 105w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20240208-Maney-Flint-029_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.4423&amp;fp-y=0.4976&amp;h=210&amp;q=75&amp;w=210&amp;s=b53768ac82c59bed6242a16233e75564 210w"
                    width="105"
